    <!-- The basic information about our app-->
    <string name="information_about_app">    This application is used for storing wine and delivering wine.
    We use Thingsee to monitor the temperature, pressure and humidity in the wine cellar to keep the
        environment being the most suitable for wine.
    We also use the position service to check the path when the staffs deliver wine to shops. \n\n
    We also use the application to monitor our own room environment, check the ideal humidity level for the room,
        as well as the suitable light level depend on working condition (play game, study or office work). \n\n
    To make the application work properly, you need to set up your own Thingsee unit, and allow it to
        measure Location (for map), Humidity, Temperature, Luminance (Light). The application was
        tested with a Thingsee unit that has location sensor update time interval of 10 second, and
        other sensors update time interval of 15 minutes.</string>
